  "detailed_description": "In a kingdom in ruins, several warriors attempt to defeat the knights of the Umberia kingdom, and you are one of these warriors. What sets you apart from the rest is that you use only a shield, no swords, spears, axes, or bows, just a good old shield.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Use your gold to acquire new shields and amulets that will change the way you face your enemies.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741320/extras/aee46373ef8c1b450c5948922c512c30.poster.avif?t=1749406706\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741320/extras/aee46373ef8c1b450c5948922c512c30.webm?t=1749406706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741320/extras/aee46373ef8c1b450c5948922c512c30.mp4?t=1749406706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Face the legendary king's knights, using your shield to deflect their powerful attacks.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741320/extras/e0f98581ac5f40919549d5155b0d1d64.poster.avif?t=1749406706\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741320/extras/e0f98581ac5f40919549d5155b0d1d64.webm?t=1749406706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741320/extras/e0f98581ac5f40919549d5155b0d1d64.mp4?t=1749406706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Explore the kingdom in ruins and find challenges to earn unique rewards.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741320/extras/6a0f5bdc2e00381979447470159b0a1e.poster.avif?t=1749406706\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741320/extras/6a0f5bdc2e00381979447470159b0a1e.webm?t=1749406706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741320/extras/6a0f5bdc2e00381979447470159b0a1e.mp4?t=1749406706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Talk to other warriors and inhabitants of the kingdom to learn more about its history.</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741320/extras/ebe1081abd7975a85405f0a1f2e66aeb.poster.avif?t=1749406706\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741320/extras/ebe1081abd7975a85405f0a1f2e66aeb.webm?t=1749406706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741320/extras/ebe1081abd7975a85405f0a1f2e66aeb.mp4?t=1749406706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
